      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION ¶ FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON. ¶ William Edward Matthews ¶ Kerferd Place, Albert Park, Melbourne ¶ Agricultural Chemist...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.09.00c </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Linnean Society of London</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Linnean Society, London, Certificates of Fellows, foreign members and associates, 1887-90.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">William Edward Matthews</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">Kerferd Place, Albert Park, Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">Agricultural Chemist</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History, especially</seg>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; "> </seg>(organic chemistry)<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">The large parentheses around</seg>
                     <seg style=""> organic chemistry </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">appear to have been added later</seg>
                     <seg style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>, Botany, and naturalization of plants for Industrial Culture, Member of the Society of Chemical Industry, Member of the Field Naturalists Club of Victoria &amp;c &amp;c<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The body of the form was apparently completed by Matthews, cf. Matthews's obligation form dated 'April 27th/88'.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">being desirous of becoming a Fellow of the LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON, we, whose names are underwritten, beg leave to recommend him to that honour.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller, M.D., F.L.S. </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">J. G. Luehmann F.L.S.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Chas French. F.L.S.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">This recommendation must be signed by Three or more Fellows.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">N.B. – The Christian name of the Candidate must be stated at length, as well as his Residence, and any special qualifications he may possess.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">This certificate was read at a General Meeting of the Society, on the</seg> 17 <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg> Novr. 1887.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>To have been read at the Society in November, the form must have been sent no later than September 1887, and it is numbered accordingly.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">The Ballot will take place on the</seg> 15 <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg> December, 1887<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annotated front: </seg>
                     <seg style="">BDJ [B. D. Jackson].</seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; "> back, in ink: </seg>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>William Edward Matthews elected 15 December 1887. </seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
